(14469, 'Asmalair 5mg 10 tab.', 'ازمالير 5 مجم 10 اقراص', '', '34', 'Montelukast', 'Hi-pharm', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Asthma.anti-inflammatory.leukotriene antagonist', '5mg', 'Montelukast is indicated for:
